Package: quackle
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Crossword game artificial intelligence and analysis tool
 Quackle is a crossword game artificial intelligence and analysis tool.
 It provides automated game analysis, strategy development, and can serve
 as a powerful AI opponent for crossword games like Scrabble.
 .
 The package includes the full Quackle UI written in Qt, along with
 the core libquackle engine and quackleio library for game data
 management and dictionary access.
